| **404 handler** | Catch-all route | Prevents Express's default HTML error page from leaking framework info |
| **Central error handler** | 4-argument middleware | Strips stack traces in production; logs full details server-side only |
| **Configurable port** | `process.env.PORT \|\| 3000` | Follows 12-factor app principles; avoids hardcoded infrastructure values |

