|---|---|---|
| No error handling middleware | 🔴 Critical | Add `(err, req, res, next)` handler |
| No security headers | 🔴 Critical | Add `helmet` |
| No rate limiting | 🔴 Critical | Add `express-rate-limit` |
| No body parsing limits | 🟡 Medium | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` |
| No input validation | 🟡 Medium | Use `express-validator` |
| Hardcoded port/host | 🟡 Medium | Use `process.env.PORT` / `HOST` |
| No graceful shutdown | 🟡 Medium | Handle `SIGTERM` |
| Unauthenticated PII endpoint | 🟢 Low/Context-dependent | Add auth middleware |

